---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
Page: 213
Author: Yuan Mei
---
Let go of desires and simply act naturally;
just do what you do.
Who knows where the clouds of the sky,
or the water of a brook,
come from or where they are going.
There is no answer, so don't bother seeking it.
